 and avoid <a href=\"#\">split-brain</a> behavior. (Plus, we hire curious people, so they generally want to know the details of what’s going on.)</p>","font-size":"18px","font_type":"400","line-height":"1.5","letter-spacing":"0px","text_color_picker":"#6f7c82","align_type":"left","max-width":"100%","check_for_resfont":"0","res-font-size":"32px","margin_css":{"top":"20px","right":"0px","bottom":"20px","left":"0px"},"padding_css":{"left":"0px","right":"0px","top":"0px","bottom":"0px"}},{"cell_id":23,"index":5,"type":"text-mod","container_id":2,"cell_container":1,"cell_identity_name":7,"content_title":"<p>We are committed to building an actively inclusive work environment that makes Stripe an excellent home for everyone—regardless of gender, sexual orientation, ethnicity, race, education, age, or other personal characteristics. We work on broadening our diversity because we think it’s simply the right thing to do. We want to include people, be a spectacular home for them to be themselves, and enable them to do great work</p>","font-size":"18px","font_type":"400","line-height":"1.5","letter-spacing":"0px","text_color_picker":"#6f7c82","align_type":"left","max-width":"100%","check_for_resfont":"0","res-font-size":"32px","margin_css":{"top":"20px","right":"0px","bottom":"20px","left":"0px"},"padding_css":{"left":"0px","right":"0px","top":"0px","bottom":"0px"}},{"cell_id":7,"index":6,"type":"text-mod","container_id":2,"cell_container":1,"cell_identity_name":7,"content_title":"<p>For more on how we work, we’ve put together this <a href=\"#\">quick guide</a> about our culture today.</p>","font-size":"18px","font_type":"400","line-height":"1.5","letter-spacing":"0px","text_color_picker":"#6f7c82","align_type":"left","max-width":"100%","check_for_resfont":"0","res-font-size":"32px","margin_css":{"top":"20px","right":"0px","bottom":"20px","left":"0px"},"padding_css":{"left":"0px","right":"0px","top":"0px","bottom":"0px"}},{"cell_id":12,"index":7,"type":"button-mod","container_i